Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lesson 3 Sorry sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to the tape then answer this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the man get his umbrella back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My coat and my umbrella please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Number five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your umbrella and your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
